	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: [Need Help] Megaman X2 Repro with 27C160</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The 27C160 is a 16-bit ROM; its address lines specify an address in 16-bit words.<br />The CX4 wants to talk to an 8-bit ROM.<br /><br />Therefore, tie /BYTE low, and connect <br />ROM A-1 to CX4 A0<br />ROM A0 to CX4 A1<br />ROM A1 to CX4 A2<br />and so on up.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


